title: Microsoft Azure AddOn: Arc State
agents: azure
catalog: cloud/Microsoft
license: GPLv2
distribution: Christopher Pommer
description:
 This check monitors the Azure Arc onboarded machine state.

 Depending on the configured service state levels for the available
 azure arc states, the service is {OK}, {WARN}, {CRIT} or {UNKNOWN}.

 You have to configure the special agent {Microsoft Azure AddOn}.

discovery:
 One service is created for the Azure Arc state.
